intent.user_query: What are the names of the customers who have opened the most service tickets, and how many tickets has each of them opened?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT c.FirstName, c.LastName, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS NumberOfTickets FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Customers c ON st.CustomerID = c.CustomerID GROUP BY c.FirstName, c.LastName ORDER BY NumberOfTickets DESC LIMIT 10;

arguments.sql: SELECT c.FirstName, c.LastName, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS NumberOfTickets FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Customers c ON st.CustomerID = c.CustomerID GROUP BY c.FirstName, c.LastName ORDER BY NumberOfTickets DESC LIMIT 10;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
